data.text:
In the real world

Willis O'Brien begins work on his film Creation. It is ultimately cancelled by RKO in favor of Merian C. Cooper's King Kong.

January

28 January: Sakyo Komatsu is born Minoru Komatsu in Osaka, Japan.

February

24 February: Sei Ikeno is born in Hokkaido, Japan.

March

2 March: Yu Fujiki is born in Tokyo Prefecture, Japan.

30 March: Yoshimitsu Banno is born in Ehime, Japan.

April

28 April: Hajime Tsuburaya, firstborn son of Eiji Tsuburaya, is born in Tokyo Prefecture, Japan.

May

May 1: The Empire State Building opens to the public.

July

6 July: Robert Dunham is born in Maine, USA.

10 July: Nick Adams is born in Pennsylvania, USA.

October

24 October: Ken Utsui is born in Tokyo Prefecture, Japan.

November

1 November: Shunsuke Kikuchi is born in Aomori, Japan.

15 November: Yoshitami Kuroiwa is born.
